about_1: PinkRent started in 2022 as a small indie team of developers looking to lower the basic living costs in the city of Gothenburg, Sweden. It's a small renting ecosystem in which people can rent out things for free or for a cost. The goal is to make sure more people can access more stuff with less boundaries.
about_2: So PinkRent was born, and so began our adventure. But along our coding journey the faced many challenges, interpersonal, technical and metaphysical ones. Challenges no one would have anticpiated at the start of a adventures such as theirs.
about_3: But this little team of developer refused to give up, they coded day, and night, to ensure the delivery of their product and a passing grade in their course. Something only few can dream of in FED21G.
about_4: The final product is the fantastic website you are visiting right now. PinkRent was created from blood, energydrinks and tears. We hope you enjoy your visit.
contact_1: Feel free to Contact us at: PinkRent@DontMail.com
startpage_1: We connect people to create economic opportunites for all. PinkRent creates inspiring experiences for our buyers and sellers, providing opportunity to grow and thrive - no matter who they are.
